<OL>
<A NAME="1"><H3>Task 1</H3></A>

<P>

Move Stub files from the Server subdirectory.

<p>
<HR WIDTH="80%">

<P>

Move the following classes into the Client subdirectory:
<pre>
LocalModel.class
RemoteModelMgrImpl_Stub.class
RemoteModelImpl_Stub.class
RemoteModelRef.class
RemoteModelMgr.class</pre>

</p>
<A NAME="2"><H3>Task 2</H3></A>

<P>

Compile all of the class files for the client.

</p>
<HR WIDTH="80%">

<P>

In a separate DOS console, go to the Client subdirectory for this exercise.
Compile all of the java files with the command:
<pre>javac *.java</pre>


<P>
This will compile all of the client classes.
<p>
<A NAME="3"><H3>Task 3</H3></A>

<P>

Run the RMI client program.

<p>
<HR WIDTH="80%">

<P>

Use the <CODE>java</CODE> program to run the server
<pre><CODE>java LocalRemoteClient</CODE></pre>

<p>
